         <div type="translation">
            <p>
                       Gaius Horten[sius] made (this) for Am[---], his dearest comrade. 
                       He was pleasant with him for 26 years. He died [---] years of age.
                    </p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>
                       The person this was dedicated to is illegible. 
                       He was the comrade (contubernalis) of the dedicator, C. Hortensius.
                       Line 6 - "obiit" (he died) is misspelled "obit"
                    </p>
         </div>
